{"tid":389449,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"電訊業世界大戰","createTime":"2017-09-06T09:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T09:35:27.000Z","uid":32485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0df0116b215c2f80284d946e40cc3996f020d092","tid":389449,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"【短兵相接】csl.劈價三成 最平月費316元無限上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本地電訊商繼續短兵相接，香港電訊（6823）宣佈，由數碼通（315）及香港寬頻（1310）客戶轉台至csl.及1010指定的「600速」服務計劃，即送「用量皇」數據組合，變相每月減150元。意味轉台至csl.最平每月316元即可享無限數據服務，劈價逾三成；至於1010亦同劈價28.6%，最平375元可享無限數據服務。現有客戶續約亦可享同樣優惠。<br />\n<br />\n繼香港寬頻上月底推月費236元的12GB數據4.5G全速月費計劃搶客後，香港電訊亦立刻反擊，送「用量皇」數據組合予由數碼通及香港寬頻轉台客。現時csl 6GB及10GB的「600速」月費連行費分別為316元及456元，變相割價32.2%及24.75%。<br />\n<br />\n至於1010，原本6GB及10GB的「600速」月費連行政費分別為375元及515元，變相割價28.6及22.6%。<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，香港寬頻現時4G無限上網Plan，連行政費每月收464元，分別較csl.及1010貴46.8%及23.7%。至於數碼通4G無限上網Plan，連行政費每月收484元，分別較csl.及1010貴53.2%及29%。<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170906&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57176330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170906%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57176330&d=cjmf4A%2BpYGFx723OlEA3xdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=ede3f5b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170906%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D57176330&h=52199d6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170906&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=57176330</a>"},{"pid":"223fc5c52c4ba80d222cefdf35f65a1f1af7c59f","tid":389449,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"再平D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc473e132b02a0313e2e0aee2bf1912e7fca5ea"